396
00:23:53,659 --> 00:23:56,095
From the start, Lee Jong Su
didn't care about Hee Su at all.

397
00:23:56,896 --> 00:23:59,098
He tormented Hee Su
to get to Chairman Choi Young Ho.

398
00:23:59,098 --> 00:24:01,167
