of the works they create...

442
00:25:58,017 --> 00:25:59,886
is silence.

443
00:25:59,886 --> 00:26:01,420
When do you think...

444
00:26:02,455 --> 00:26:04,557
architects step out of the silence...

445
00:26:04,557 --> 00:26:06,659
you just spoke of, Mr. Ryu?

446
00:26:06,659 --> 00:26:08,794
I believe silence must continue.

447
00:26:08,794 --> 00:26:09,629
But...

448
00:26:10,563 --> 00:26:14,634
only through communion and communication
between the building and people...

449
00:26:14,634 --> 00:26:15,535
can one...

450
00:26:15,535 --> 00:26:17,670
finally step out of that silence.

451
00:26:21,741 --> 00:26:24,477
There's something
people are mistaken about.

452
00:26:25,545 --> 00:26:26,712
Because they focus...

453
00:26:28,014 --> 00:26:30,049
only on a building's exterior
and function,

454
00:26:30,049 --> 00:26:32,185
