456
00:26:34,921 --> 00:26:37,190
Could you tell me
what direction you're headed in,

457
00:26:38,591 --> 00:26:39,625
Mr. Ryu?

458
00:26:41,227 --> 00:26:43,329
"There is no such thing as architecture,"

459
00:26:44,697 --> 00:26:45,965
