508
00:28:52,859 --> 00:28:53,659
Are you rich?

509
00:28:57,296 --> 00:28:58,698
I'll give you as much as you want.

510
00:28:58,698 --> 00:28:59,932
Not a penny less.

511
00:28:59,932 --> 00:29:02,735
